cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper proposes a Bayesian reward learning algorithm for imitation learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm is applied to control problems, which suggests the category of robotics (cs.RO). The authors also evaluate their approach on Atari games, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and potentially system and control (cs.SY) aspects.
